	<section class="section" id="faq">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header fade-in">
				<h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
				<p>Quick answers to help you get started.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq__list">
				<div class="faq-item fade-in">
					<button class="faq-item__question">
						How long is the free trial?
						<svg
							class="faq-item__icon"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
						>
							<path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
						</svg>
					</button>
					<div class="faq-item__answer">
						<p>
							Every plan includes a full-featured 14-day free trial. No credit card required to
							start. You get access to all features in your chosen plan during the trial period.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item fade-in">
					<button class="faq-item__question">
						Can I switch plans later?
						<svg
							class="faq-item__icon"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
						>
							<path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
						</svg>
					</button>
					<div class="faq-item__answer">
						<p>
							Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. When upgrading, you get
							immediate access to the new features. Downgrades take effect at the end of your
							current billing cycle.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item fade-in">
					<button class="faq-item__question">
						Where is my data stored?
						<svg
							class="faq-item__icon"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
						>
							<path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
						</svg>
					</button>
					<div class="faq-item__answer">
						<p>
							Your data is stored in the region closest to you. We have data centres in Mumbai
							(India), Bahrain (Middle East), Singapore (Southeast Asia), Frankfurt (Europe), New
							York (Americas), Sydney (Australia), and Cape Town (Africa). All data is encrypted at
							rest and in transit.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item fade-in">
					<button class="faq-item__question">
						Is my data secure and compliant?
						<svg
							class="faq-item__icon"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
						>
							<path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
						</svg>
					</button>
					<div class="faq-item__answer">
						<p>
							Absolutely. Lucoze is built with healthcare-grade security including end-to-end
							encryption, role-based access control, audit logging, and automated backups. We are
							HIPAA-ready with regional compliance. <span data-region-show="in">ABDM/ABHA integration for Indian facilities.</span><span data-region-show="ae">NABIDH and NPHIES compliant for GCC operations.</span><span data-region-show="sg">NEHR-ready for Singapore health records.</span><span data-region-show="au,intl">HL7 FHIR and ICD-10 standards compliant.</span>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item fade-in">
					<button class="faq-item__question">
						Do I need to install anything?
						<svg
							class="faq-item__icon"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
						>
							<path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
						</svg>
					</button>
					<div class="faq-item__answer">
						<p>
							No. Lucoze is a fully cloud-based platform. All you need is a web browser. It works on
							desktop, tablet, and mobile devices. No downloads, no IT team required.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item fade-in">
					<button class="faq-item__question">
						What payment methods do you accept?
						<svg
							class="faq-item__icon"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
						>
							<path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
						</svg>
					</button>
					<div class="faq-item__answer">
						<p>
							For India, we accept all major payment methods via Razorpay — credit/debit cards, UPI,
							net banking, and wallets. For international customers, we accept credit/debit cards
							via Stripe.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-item fade-in">
					<button class="faq-item__question">
						Can I get a custom domain?
						<svg
							class="faq-item__icon"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
						>
							<path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
						</svg>
					</button>
					<div class="faq-item__answer">
						<p>
							Yes! Every workspace gets a free subdomain (yourname.lucoze.com). You can also add
							your own custom domain as an add-on for a small monthly fee.
						</p>
